---
title: Pan-Seared John Dory & Sesame Greens with Coconut Lemongrass Sauce & Garlic Rice
description: Delicate pan-seared John dory meets vibrant sesame-kissed greens in this elegant yet effortless dish. The real star? A silky coconut lemongrass sauce that’s bursting with fragrant, citrusy goodness. Served over fluffy, garlicky rice, every bite is a perfect balance of rich, bright, and utterly satisfying flavours.
